    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120980/extras/7ccc8524e159d2fb1466e4ec674a6d7b.poster.avif?t=1747053182\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120980/extras/7ccc8524e159d2fb1466e4ec674a6d7b.webm?t=1747053182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120980/extras/7ccc8524e159d2fb1466e4ec674a6d7b.mp4?t=1747053182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>传说中的英雄<strong>Jaxx Fury</strong>，在多年流亡后回到故乡。凭着他勇敢且坚定的精神，他成为对抗黑暗巫师<strong>Nachtengel</strong>的最后希望。在阴影逼近和危险增加之际，Jaxx必须挺身而出，拯救他的人民，实现曾经的梦想和命运。<br><br>操控我们的英雄，挥舞他的传奇吉他作为武器，迎战成群的敌人，征服各种挑战障碍！探索充满动态环境的多彩关卡，寻找隐藏的1UP。<br><br><strong>特点：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 快节奏的重金属音乐<br></li><li> 创新的关卡，让玩家体验不同的氛围<br></li><li> 难度不同的挑战性障碍<br></li><li> 令人愤怒的最终boss！</li></ul><br>让<strong>Nala</strong>引导你到<strong>Nachtengel</strong>，并一劳永逸地击败他！在这被诅咒的城市迷宫中前行，面对许多不同的障碍。<br><br>不要气馁！无论多么困难，都不要放弃。城市的命运依赖于你！<br>...最后，永远朝着大门前进！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120980/extras/01b1e33562adde08a3bf150decf9bf47.poster.avif?t=1747053182\" width=600 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120980/extras/01b1e33562adde08a3bf150decf9bf47.webm?t=1747053182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120980/extras/01b1e33562adde08a3bf150decf9bf47.mp4?t=1747053182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
